        "stop": "North Bay",
        "category": "Nature",
        "desc": "North Bay's stunning Lake Nipissing waterfront is a must-visit. Shabogesic Beach offers supervised summer swimming. The Heritage Railway and Carousel Company on Memorial Drive has a hand-crafted carousel and miniature train ride along the lake - kids absolutely love it. The Dock Shoppe Ice Cream Parlour sits right on the pier. Chief Commanda II scenic cruise ship runs Lake Nipissing tours. In winter the frozen lake hosts ice fishing, cross-country skiing, snowmobiling, and the biennial Ice Follies art festival. Beautiful at every season.",
